Have fun on your vacation, Shomin.

::Proto::

Proto turns around as Stranato and co. enter, looking at the three (I'm 
assuming that Infectra is there, if not, then Proto is looking at two).

"Ah, there you are," he says, looking at Stranato, "Allright, I still need to 
assign you quarters."

He looks at the bots. "How many will you need?"
